    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in The Arts yesterday about the leading movies in ticket sales over the weekend misstated the given name of the vice chairman of Lionsgate, who commented on the recent decline in sales for horror films like ''Hostel: Part II,'' which ranked sixth over the weekend. He is Michael Burns, not Mark.</p>
      </block>
